            "id": "https://huobingnan.github.io/2023/01/29/Maven-Assembly-Plugin/",
            "url": "https://huobingnan.github.io/2023/01/29/Maven-Assembly-Plugin/",
            "title": "Maven Assembly Plugin",
            "date_published": "2023-01-28T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/css/lightgallery.min.css\" /><div class=\".article-gallery\"><h2 id=\"1-Maven打包\"><a href=\"#1-Maven打包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. Maven打包\"></a>1. Maven打包</h2><p>Maven打包发生在生命周期的<em>package</em>阶段，默认情况下Maven打包是不会伴随项目的依赖一起发布的。如果需要在发布的<em>jar</em>包或者<em>war</em>包中添加项目的依赖项，则需要借助Maven的一个原生插件<em>maven-assembly-plugin</em>。</p>\n<p>关于Maven Assembly Plugin的具体使用可以查看Maven官网的文档：<a href=\"https://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-assembly-plugin/\">Maven Assembly Plugin</a>。</p>\n<p>当然，上述插件在打包项目依赖的jar包条目和一些简单资源项时，是十分便利够用的。如果涉及更加复杂的资源条目打包或者更加精细的资源控制时，Maven官方推荐使用<em>maven-shade-plugin</em>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-Maven-Assembly插件\"><a href=\"#2-Maven-Assembly插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. Maven Assembly插件\"></a>2. Maven Assembly插件</h2><p>Maven Assembly插件的作用是组合项目的构建输出（包括依赖项、子模块和文档等）并将其压缩到单个文件中。文件的类型并不局限于<em>jar</em>，也可以是<em>zip</em>、<em>tar</em>、<em>tar.gz</em>、<em>dir</em>和<em>war</em>等。</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-在项目中引入插件\"><a href=\"#2-1-在项目中引入插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1 在项目中引入插件\"></a>2.1 在项目中引入插件</h3><p>在<em>pom.xml</em>文件中的<code>&lt;build&gt; &lt;plugins&gt;</code>条目中添加插件坐标。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><figcaption><span>在pom.xml中引入Maven Assembly Plugin</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">project</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">build</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugins</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 引入maven-assembly-plugin --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>maven-assembly-plugin<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">plugins</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">build</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">project</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"2-2-使用预定义描述符\"><a href=\"#2-2-使用预定义描述符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2 使用预定义描述符\"></a>2.2 使用预定义描述符</h3><p>预定义描述符（prefabricated assembly descriptors)是Assembly插件为了方便打包引入的一系列可复用的操作集合。在使用预定义描述符的情况下，只进行简略的配置即可完成资源的打包整合工作。</p>\n<p>Assembly插件提供了四个预定义描述符：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><em>bin</em></li>\n<li><em>jar-with-dependencies</em></li>\n<li><em>src</em></li>\n<li><em>project</em></li>\n</ol>\n<p>若打包中想要添加依赖项，最简便的方法就是使用<em>jar-with-dependencies</em>描述符。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><figcaption><span>配置预定义描述符</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>maven-assembly-plugin<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRefs</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span>jar-with-dependencies<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRefs</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>若想要构建可执行jar包，则需要进一步配置jar包的清单文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><figcaption><span>配置jar包清单项</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>maven-assembly-plugin<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">archive</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">manifest</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 在mainClass中指定入口类的全限定类名 --&gt;</span>\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">mainClass</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">mainClass</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">manifest</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">archive</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRefs</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span>jar-with-dependencies<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRefs</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如果想要将源代码打包为压缩文件作为项目发布的条目，则可以使用<em>src</em>描述符。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><figcaption><span>源代码打包</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>maven-assembly-plugin<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRefs</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span>jar-with-dependencies<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span>src<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRefs</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>src默认会将项目的源代码和资源文件进行压缩，得到诸如<em>zip</em>和<em>tar.gz</em>格式类型的压缩包，便于源代码的发布。</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-3-绑定生命周期\"><a href=\"#2-3-绑定生命周期\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.3 绑定生命周期\"></a>2.3 绑定生命周期</h3><p><em>maven-assembly-plugin</em>只会将项目构建输出目录下的资源进行整合打包。如果项目还没有被编译，那么执行此插件并不会得到预期的效果。因此将插件的执行绑定到maven的一个生命周期执行环节是十分明智的选择。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84.png\" class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84.png\"></a></p>\n<p>在没有编译整个项目的情况下，执行<code>mvn assembly:single</code></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8Cassembly.png\" class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8Cassembly.png\"></a></p>\n<p>可以看到虽然得到了一个jar包文件，但是<em>target</em>目录下并没有源代码的编译输出目录<em>classes</em>。显然这个jar包文件也是不完整的，它并没有包含项目源码的编译结果。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209assembly%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA.png\" class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209assembly%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA.png\"></a></p>\n<p>从执行的结果也可以看出，jar包中并没有包含<em>pom.xml</em>中配置的主类</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209jar.png\" class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209jar.png\"></a></p>\n<p>综上所述，我们期望插件在Maven构建过程中一个恰当的生命周期中被执行，这样可以准确地得到预期的输出。这就需要将插件的执行和Maven构建生命周期相绑定。</p>\n<p>显然，我们期望<em>maven-assembly-plugin</em>在项目被编译完之后，尤其是在Maven生命周期的打包阶段被执行。为此，需要在插件的配置项中添加如下规则配置：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><figcaption><span>绑定Assembly插件的生命周期</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>maven-assembly-plugin<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRefs</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span>jar-with-dependencies<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRef</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">descriptorRefs</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">configuration</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 配置插件的执行时机 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">executions</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">execution</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">id</span>&gt;</span>package-with-deps<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">id</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 配置在打包阶段执行此插件 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">phase</span>&gt;</span>package<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">phase</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">goals</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 配置插件的执行目标 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">goal</span>&gt;</span>single<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">goal</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">goals</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">execution</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">executions</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">plugin</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>绑定完生命周期之后，在构建时并不需要显式调用插件执行，插件会在绑定的阶段自动执行，完成它的使命。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84.png\" class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84.png\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8Cassembly.png\" class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/huobingnan/ImageStore/main/220209%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8Cassembly.png\"></a></p>\n</div><script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/js/lightgallery.min.js\"></script><script>if (typeof lightGallery !== 'undefined') {\n        var options = {\n            selector: '.gallery-item'\n        };\n        lightGallery(document.getElementsByClassName('.article-gallery')[0], options);\n        }</script>",
